                    <span>This book could have been written about me.  I am a stuggling manager who is having a tough time juggling everything. Unfortunately, I do not have a "Tony" to help. In fact, my boss needs to read this book too.
<br />
<br />I highly recommend Monday Morning Leadership and Monday Morning Leadership for Women.  The women version has some of the same concepts in it but is very good as well.
<br />
<br />I would love to find someone like Tony who would invest their time and wisdom with me.</span>
                  
              
